{"tid":1198663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十一號晚十一點 立會見 請廣傳","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:38:17.000Z","uid":23993,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b622973db1b53d20af8840e65f73c7383aaa1a","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"我知經過尋晚之後 肯放低身段帶頭衝被塔嗰班 告士打道俾速龍趕埋牆角投降嗰班 未必再可以出嚟<br />\n但你甘心咩？甘心再一次輸得一敗塗地咩？<br />\n再一次輸俾呢個蠻橫無理 全港8分1嘅人口100萬人上街都可以當你冇到嘅極權咩？<br />\n我唔甘心呀 我要贏呀屌佢老母 哪怕事後幾多鬼呀收咗錢呀一句句一刀刀插埋嚟 我就係想贏番次<br />\n話掂都係要佢撤 做乜仲要等大會照開<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定要係二讀前就做嘢<br />\n等民陣嗰班搞得嚟 都過咗啦戇鳩<br />\n我知唔夠人嘅話 今次行動形同自殺<br />\n但我會唔會去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會！！！</span><br />\n我夠膽輸賭 我唔會係唯一一個<br />\n<br />\n唔好再設多餘嘅心理關口俾自己 唔肯整污糟雙手 就乜柒都換唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Don't cry to quit! <br />\nYou already in pain, you already hurt! <br />\nGET A REWARD FROM IT!</span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個po嘅手足 請用你哋嘅方法 將呢個消息廣傳開去 求吓你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"280b61f0c44cbcd0cd90d5b385e09bd2c4407e18","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1efaec9361178b7c855e28e708b683de195703e5","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"737ac9cff2e3a6dad69e59acfbe8459ead07c718","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ad6aab23b7f959afe7c952fe3accb697e8122ad","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:00:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96bcb4f6c87189a0e6e8e90f39bd193268b9b552","tid":1198663,"uid":232082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZecI195bvQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=cbb36d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ</a><br />\n1:38 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hor_hJqNoS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhor_hJqNoS0&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=60148051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hor_hJqNoS0</a><br />\n0:11 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtlaOekIQbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrtlaOekIQbU&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=e8bffe51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtlaOekIQbU</a><br />\n1:27 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DNTsCcDlDmI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDNTsCcDlDmI&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=dcca8cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DNTsCcDlDmI</a><br />\n1:54 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講咩啲狗打份工 <br />\n你要甘心淪為政權打壓人民既工具 你同時要承受返你咁樣做既惡果<br />\n你 冇 得 怨 <br />\n屌 你 老 母<br />\n死 都 冇 得 怨<br />\n<br />\n各位記住保持清醒頭腦 每一刻都要知道自己做緊咩<br />\n點樣走位 點樣救人 點樣部署下一刻<br />\n唔好剩係跟住人走 因為你身邊既人可以隨時需要你幫忙<br />\n我地要有自主意識 我地要冷靜過啲狗<br />\n<br />\nbe water my friend<br />\n港人加油"},{"pid":"fd9110f5a686f96b1c23848c66051fe2ec185491","tid":1198663,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"191b869412b82ad464ac4e3e872cb6df230a5c48","tid":1198663,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re